data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Male or female participant must be between 18-50 (inclusive) years of age;
* Meet criteria for plasma donation\*;
* Available for clinic follow-up through Day 99 and one additional follow-up call on Day 181 (±14 days);
* Agrees not to receive any vaccine from day of enrollment

Inclusion Criteria:

* HIV RNA ≥5000 c/ml

Exclusion Criteria:

* Any antiretroviral therapy within 30 days prior to screening;
* Women of Childbearing potential (WOCBP) unwilling or unable to use an acceptable method to avoid pregnancy for the entire study and for up to 8 weeks after the study;
